{
  "video_id": "OkKhI6-t40w",
  "title": "His Holiness the Karmapa: The technology of the heart",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "Tyler Dewar: The way I feel right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "is that all of the other speakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "have said exactly what I wanted to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "And it seems that the only thing left for me to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "is to thank you all for your kindness."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 58260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "TD: But maybe in the spirit"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 62260.0,
      "text": "of appreciating the kindness of you all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 64259.0,
      "text": "I could share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 64260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66260.0,
      "text": "a little story about myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "TD: From the time I was very young, onward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "I was given"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "a lot of different responsibilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "and it always seemed to me, when I was young,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "that everything was laid out before me."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "All of the plans for me were already made."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "I was given the clothes that I needed to wear"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "and told where I needed to be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "given these very precious"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "and holy looking robes to wear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "with the understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "that it was something sacred or important."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 187260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "TD: But before that kind of formal lifestyle happened for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "I was living in eastern Tibet with my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "And when I was seven years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "all of a sudden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "a search party arrived at my home."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "They were looking the next Karmapa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "and I noticed they were talking to my mom and dad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 210260.0,
      "text": "and the news came to me that they were telling me"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 210260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "that I was the Karmapa."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 212260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "And these days, people ask me a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "how did that feel."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "How did that feel when they came and whisked you away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "and your lifestyle completely changed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "And what I mostly say is that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "at that time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "it was a pretty interesting idea to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "I thought that things would be pretty fun"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "and there would be more things to play with."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "TD: But it didn&#39;t turn out to be so fun and entertaining,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "as I thought it would have been."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "I was placed"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 306260.0,
      "text": "in a pretty strictly controlled environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 306260.0,
      "end_time": 308260.0,
      "text": "And immediately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 308260.0,
      "end_time": 310260.0,
      "text": "a lot of different responsibilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 310260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "in terms of my education and so forth, were heaped upon me."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "I was separated, largely, from my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "including my mother and father."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 319260.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t have have many personal friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 319260.0,
      "end_time": 321260.0,
      "text": "to spend time with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "but I was expected to perform"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "these prescribed duties."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "So it turned out that my fantasy"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 330260.0,
      "text": "about an entertaining life of being the Karmapa"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 330260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "wasn&#39;t going to come true."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 332260.0,
      "end_time": 334260.0,
      "text": "It more felt to be the case to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 334260.0,
      "end_time": 337260.0,
      "text": "that I was being treated like a statue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 337260.0,
      "end_time": 340260.0,
      "text": "and I was to sit in one place"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 340260.0,
      "end_time": 342260.0,
      "text": "like a statue would."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "TD: Nevertheless, I felt that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "even though I&#39;ve been separated from my loved ones --"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 399260.0,
      "text": "and, of course, now I&#39;m even further away."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 399260.0,
      "end_time": 401260.0,
      "text": "When I was 14, I escaped from Tibet"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 401260.0,
      "end_time": 403260.0,
      "text": "and became even further removed"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 403260.0,
      "end_time": 405260.0,
      "text": "from my mother and father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 405260.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "my relatives, my friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 409260.0,
      "text": "and my homeland."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 409260.0,
      "end_time": 411260.0,
      "text": "But nevertheless,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 411260.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no real sense of separation from me in my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 414260.0,
      "end_time": 417260.0,
      "text": "in terms of the love that I feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 419260.0,
      "text": "for these people."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 419260.0,
      "end_time": 422260.0,
      "text": "I feel, still, a very strong connection of love"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 422260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "for all of these people"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "and for the land."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "TD: And I still do"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 456260.0,
      "text": "get to keep in touch with my mother and father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 456260.0,
      "end_time": 458260.0,
      "text": "albeit infrequently."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 458260.0,
      "end_time": 460260.0,
      "text": "I talk to my mother"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 460260.0,
      "end_time": 462260.0,
      "text": "once in a blue moon on the telephone."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "And my experience is that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "when I&#39;m talking to her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 468260.0,
      "text": "with every second that passes"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 468260.0,
      "end_time": 470260.0,
      "text": "during our conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 470260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "the feeling of love that binds us"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 476260.0,
      "text": "is bringing us closer and closer together."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 548260.0,
      "end_time": 550260.0,
      "text": "TD: So those were just a few remarks"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 550260.0,
      "end_time": 552260.0,
      "text": "about my personal background."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 552260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "And in terms of other things that I wanted to share with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 557260.0,
      "text": "in terms of ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 560260.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s wonderful to have a situation like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 560260.0,
      "end_time": 563260.0,
      "text": "where so many people from different backgrounds and places"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 563260.0,
      "end_time": 565260.0,
      "text": "can come together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 565260.0,
      "end_time": 567260.0,
      "text": "exchange their ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 567260.0,
      "end_time": 570260.0,
      "text": "and form relationships of friendship with each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 570260.0,
      "end_time": 572260.0,
      "text": "And I think that&#39;s symbolic"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 574260.0,
      "text": "of what we&#39;re seeing in the world in general,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 574260.0,
      "end_time": 576260.0,
      "text": "that the world is becoming smaller and smaller,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 576260.0,
      "end_time": 579260.0,
      "text": "and that all of the peoples in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 579260.0,
      "end_time": 582260.0,
      "text": "are enjoying more opportunities for connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 583260.0,
      "end_time": 585260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s wonderful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 585260.0,
      "end_time": 587260.0,
      "text": "but we should also remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 590260.0,
      "text": "that we should have a similar process happening on the inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 590260.0,
      "end_time": 592260.0,
      "text": "Along with outward development"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 592260.0,
      "end_time": 594260.0,
      "text": "and increase of opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 594260.0,
      "end_time": 597260.0,
      "text": "there should be inward development"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 597260.0,
      "end_time": 600260.0,
      "text": "and deepening of our heart connections"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 600260.0,
      "end_time": 603260.0,
      "text": "as well as our outward connections."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 604260.0,
      "end_time": 606260.0,
      "text": "So we spoke and we heard some"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 606260.0,
      "end_time": 608260.0,
      "text": "about design this week."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 608260.0,
      "end_time": 610260.0,
      "text": "I think that it&#39;s important for us to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 610260.0,
      "end_time": 612260.0,
      "text": "that we need"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 612260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "to keep pushing forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 616260.0,
      "text": "on the endeavor"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 616260.0,
      "end_time": 618260.0,
      "text": "of the design of the heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 618260.0,
      "end_time": 620260.0,
      "text": "We heard a lot about technology this week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 620260.0,
      "end_time": 622260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s important for us to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 622260.0,
      "end_time": 625260.0,
      "text": "to invest a lot of our energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 625260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "in improving the technology of the heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 647260.0,
      "end_time": 649260.0,
      "text": "TD: So, even though I&#39;m somewhat happy"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 649260.0,
      "end_time": 652260.0,
      "text": "about the wonderful developments that are happening in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 652260.0,
      "end_time": 655260.0,
      "text": "still, I feel a sense of impediment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 655260.0,
      "end_time": 657260.0,
      "text": "when it comes"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 657260.0,
      "end_time": 659260.0,
      "text": "to the ability that we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 659260.0,
      "end_time": 662260.0,
      "text": "to connect with each other on a heart-to-heart, or a mind-to-mind, level."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 662260.0,
      "end_time": 665260.0,
      "text": "I feel that there are some things"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 665260.0,
      "end_time": 667260.0,
      "text": "that are getting in the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 703260.0,
      "end_time": 705260.0,
      "text": "TC: My relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 705260.0,
      "end_time": 708260.0,
      "text": "to this concept of heart-to-heart connection, or mind-to-mind connection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 708260.0,
      "end_time": 710260.0,
      "text": "is an interesting one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 710260.0,
      "end_time": 712260.0,
      "text": "because, as a spiritual leader, I&#39;m always attempting"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 712260.0,
      "end_time": 714260.0,
      "text": "to open my heart to others"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 714260.0,
      "end_time": 716260.0,
      "text": "and offer myself up"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 716260.0,
      "end_time": 718260.0,
      "text": "for heart-to-heart and mind-to-mind connections"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 718260.0,
      "end_time": 720260.0,
      "text": "in a genuine way with other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 720260.0,
      "end_time": 722260.0,
      "text": "but at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 722260.0,
      "end_time": 724260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve always been advised"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 724260.0,
      "end_time": 726260.0,
      "text": "that I need to emphasize intelligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 726260.0,
      "end_time": 728260.0,
      "text": "over the heart-to-heart connections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 728260.0,
      "end_time": 732260.0,
      "text": "because, being someone in a position like mine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 732260.0,
      "end_time": 735260.0,
      "text": "if I don&#39;t rely primarily on intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 735260.0,
      "end_time": 738260.0,
      "text": "then something dangerous may happen to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 739260.0,
      "end_time": 742260.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s an interesting paradox at play there."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 745260.0,
      "end_time": 748260.0,
      "text": "But I had a really striking experience once,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 748260.0,
      "end_time": 750260.0,
      "text": "when a group from Afghanistan"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 750260.0,
      "end_time": 752260.0,
      "text": "came to visit me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 752260.0,
      "end_time": 755260.0,
      "text": "and we had a really interesting conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 850260.0,
      "end_time": 853260.0,
      "text": "TD: So we ended up talking about the Bamiyan Buddhas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 853260.0,
      "end_time": 855260.0,
      "text": "which, as you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 855260.0,
      "end_time": 858260.0,
      "text": "were destroyed some years ago in Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 859260.0,
      "end_time": 861260.0,
      "text": "But the basis of our conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 861260.0,
      "end_time": 863260.0,
      "text": "was the different approach to spirituality"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 863260.0,
      "end_time": 865260.0,
      "text": "on the part of the Muslim"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 865260.0,
      "end_time": 867260.0,
      "text": "and Buddhist traditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 867260.0,
      "end_time": 869260.0,
      "text": "Of course, in Muslim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 869260.0,
      "end_time": 872260.0,
      "text": "because of the teachings around the concept of idolatry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 872260.0,
      "end_time": 874260.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t find as many"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 874260.0,
      "end_time": 876260.0,
      "text": "physical representations of divinity"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 876260.0,
      "end_time": 878260.0,
      "text": "or of spiritual liberation"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 878260.0,
      "end_time": 880260.0,
      "text": "as you do in the Buddhist tradition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 880260.0,
      "end_time": 883260.0,
      "text": "where, of course, there are many statues of the Buddha"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 883260.0,
      "end_time": 886260.0,
      "text": "that are highly revered."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 888260.0,
      "end_time": 890260.0,
      "text": "So, we were talking about the differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 890260.0,
      "end_time": 892260.0,
      "text": "between the traditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 892260.0,
      "end_time": 894260.0,
      "text": "and what many people perceived"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 894260.0,
      "end_time": 897260.0,
      "text": "as the tragedy of the destruction of the Bamiyan Buddhas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 897260.0,
      "end_time": 899260.0,
      "text": "but I offered the suggestion"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 899260.0,
      "end_time": 902260.0,
      "text": "that perhaps we could look at this in a positive way."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 903260.0,
      "end_time": 906260.0,
      "text": "What we saw in the destruction of the Bamiyan Buddhas"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 910260.0,
      "end_time": 913260.0,
      "text": "was the depletion of matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 913260.0,
      "end_time": 915260.0,
      "text": "some solid substance"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 915260.0,
      "end_time": 917260.0,
      "text": "falling down and disintegrating."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 917260.0,
      "end_time": 919260.0,
      "text": "Maybe we could look at that to be more similar"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 919260.0,
      "end_time": 921260.0,
      "text": "to the falling of the Berlin Wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 921260.0,
      "end_time": 923260.0,
      "text": "where a divide"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 923260.0,
      "end_time": 926260.0,
      "text": "that had kept two types of people apart"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 926260.0,
      "end_time": 928260.0,
      "text": "had collapsed and opened up a door"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 928260.0,
      "end_time": 930260.0,
      "text": "for further communication."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 930260.0,
      "end_time": 932260.0,
      "text": "So I think that, in this way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 932260.0,
      "end_time": 934260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s always possible for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 934260.0,
      "end_time": 937260.0,
      "text": "to derive something positive"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 937260.0,
      "end_time": 940260.0,
      "text": "that can help us understand one another better."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 980260.0,
      "end_time": 982260.0,
      "text": "TD: So, with regard to the development"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 982260.0,
      "end_time": 984260.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;ve been talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 984260.0,
      "end_time": 986260.0,
      "text": "here at this conference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 986260.0,
      "end_time": 988260.0,
      "text": "I really feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 988260.0,
      "end_time": 991260.0,
      "text": "that the development that we make"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 991260.0,
      "end_time": 993260.0,
      "text": "shouldn&#39;t create a further burden"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 993260.0,
      "end_time": 995260.0,
      "text": "for us as human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 995260.0,
      "end_time": 997260.0,
      "text": "but should be used"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 997260.0,
      "end_time": 1000260.0,
      "text": "to improve"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 1000260.0,
      "end_time": 1002260.0,
      "text": "our fundamental lifestyle"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 1002260.0,
      "end_time": 1005260.0,
      "text": "of how we live in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 1096260.0,
      "end_time": 1098260.0,
      "text": "TD: Of course, I rejoice"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 1098260.0,
      "end_time": 1101260.0,
      "text": "in the development and the growth and the rise"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 1101260.0,
      "end_time": 1104260.0,
      "text": "of the noble land of India, the great country of India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 1104260.0,
      "end_time": 1106260.0,
      "text": "but at the same time, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 1106260.0,
      "end_time": 1109260.0,
      "text": "as some of us have acknowledged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 1109260.0,
      "end_time": 1111260.0,
      "text": "we need to be aware"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 1111260.0,
      "end_time": 1114260.0,
      "text": "that some aspects of this rise"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 1114260.0,
      "end_time": 1117260.0,
      "text": "are coming at the cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 1117260.0,
      "end_time": 1119260.0,
      "text": "of the very ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 1119260.0,
      "end_time": 1121260.0,
      "text": "on which we stand."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 1121260.0,
      "end_time": 1124260.0,
      "text": "So, as we are climbing the tree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 1124260.0,
      "end_time": 1126260.0,
      "text": "some of the things that we&#39;re doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 1126260.0,
      "end_time": 1128260.0,
      "text": "in order to climb the tree"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 1128260.0,
      "end_time": 1130260.0,
      "text": "are actually undermining"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 1130260.0,
      "end_time": 1132260.0,
      "text": "the tree&#39;s very root."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 1132260.0,
      "end_time": 1134260.0,
      "text": "And so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 1134260.0,
      "end_time": 1136260.0,
      "text": "what I think it comes down to"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 1136260.0,
      "end_time": 1140260.0,
      "text": "is a question of, not only having information of what&#39;s going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 1140260.0,
      "end_time": 1143260.0,
      "text": "but paying attention to that"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 1143260.0,
      "end_time": 1146260.0,
      "text": "and letting that shift our motivation"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 1146260.0,
      "end_time": 1149260.0,
      "text": "to become more sincere"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 1149260.0,
      "end_time": 1152260.0,
      "text": "and genuinely positive."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 1153260.0,
      "end_time": 1155260.0,
      "text": "We have hear, this week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 1155260.0,
      "end_time": 1159260.0,
      "text": "about the horrible sufferings, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 1159260.0,
      "end_time": 1162260.0,
      "text": "that so many women of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 1162260.0,
      "end_time": 1164260.0,
      "text": "are enduring day-to-day."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 1164260.0,
      "end_time": 1166260.0,
      "text": "We have that information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 1166260.0,
      "end_time": 1168260.0,
      "text": "but what often happens to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 1168260.0,
      "end_time": 1171260.0,
      "text": "is that we don&#39;t really choose to pay attention to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 1171260.0,
      "end_time": 1173260.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t really choose to allow that"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 1173260.0,
      "end_time": 1176260.0,
      "text": "to cause there to be a shift in our hearts."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 1176260.0,
      "end_time": 1178260.0,
      "text": "So I think the way forward for the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 1178260.0,
      "end_time": 1182260.0,
      "text": "one that will bring the path of outer development"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 1182260.0,
      "end_time": 1185260.0,
      "text": "in harmony"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 1187260.0,
      "end_time": 1190260.0,
      "text": "with the real root of happiness --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 1190260.0,
      "end_time": 1192260.0,
      "text": "is that we allow"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 1192260.0,
      "end_time": 1194260.0,
      "text": "the information that we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 1194260.0,
      "end_time": 1197260.0,
      "text": "to really make a change in our heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 1245260.0,
      "end_time": 1247260.0,
      "text": "TD: So I think that sincere motivation"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 1247260.0,
      "end_time": 1250260.0,
      "text": "is very important for our future well-being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 1250260.0,
      "end_time": 1253260.0,
      "text": "or deep sense of well-being as humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 1253260.0,
      "end_time": 1256260.0,
      "text": "and I think that means sinking in"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 1256260.0,
      "end_time": 1258260.0,
      "text": "to whatever it is you&#39;re doing now."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 1258260.0,
      "end_time": 1260260.0,
      "text": "Whatever work you&#39;re trying to do now to benefit the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 1260260.0,
      "end_time": 1262260.0,
      "text": "sink into that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 1262260.0,
      "end_time": 1264260.0,
      "text": "get a full taste of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 1300260.0,
      "end_time": 1302260.0,
      "text": "TD: So, since we&#39;ve been here this week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 1302260.0,
      "end_time": 1306260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve taken millions of breaths, collectively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 1307260.0,
      "end_time": 1309260.0,
      "text": "and perhaps we haven&#39;t witnessed"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 1309260.0,
      "end_time": 1311260.0,
      "text": "any course changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 1311260.0,
      "end_time": 1313260.0,
      "text": "happening in our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 1313260.0,
      "end_time": 1316260.0,
      "text": "but we often miss the very subtle changes."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 1316260.0,
      "end_time": 1319260.0,
      "text": "And I think"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 1319260.0,
      "end_time": 1321260.0,
      "text": "that sometimes we develop"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 1321260.0,
      "end_time": 1323260.0,
      "text": "grand concepts"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 1323260.0,
      "end_time": 1325260.0,
      "text": "of what happiness"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 1325260.0,
      "end_time": 1327260.0,
      "text": "might look like for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 1327260.0,
      "end_time": 1329260.0,
      "text": "but that, if we pay attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 1329260.0,
      "end_time": 1332260.0,
      "text": "we can see that there are little symbols of happiness"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 1332260.0,
      "end_time": 1334260.0,
      "text": "in every breath that we take."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 1401260.0,
      "end_time": 1404260.0,
      "text": "TD: So, every one of you who has come here"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 1404260.0,
      "end_time": 1406260.0,
      "text": "is so talented,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 1406260.0,
      "end_time": 1409260.0,
      "text": "and you have so much to offer to the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 1410260.0,
      "end_time": 1414260.0,
      "text": "I think it would be a good note to conclude on then"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 1414260.0,
      "end_time": 1417260.0,
      "text": "to just take a moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 1417260.0,
      "end_time": 1419260.0,
      "text": "to appreciate how fortunate we are"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 1419260.0,
      "end_time": 1422260.0,
      "text": "to have come together in this way and exchanged ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 1422260.0,
      "end_time": 1424260.0,
      "text": "and really form a strong aspiration"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 1424260.0,
      "end_time": 1426260.0,
      "text": "and energy within ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 1426260.0,
      "end_time": 1428260.0,
      "text": "that we will take the good"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 1428260.0,
      "end_time": 1430260.0,
      "text": "that has come from this conference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 1430260.0,
      "end_time": 1433260.0,
      "text": "the momentum, the positivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 1433260.0,
      "end_time": 1435260.0,
      "text": "and we will spread that and plant it"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 1435260.0,
      "end_time": 1438260.0,
      "text": "in all of the corners of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 1458260.0,
      "end_time": 1461260.0,
      "text": "His Holiness the Karmapa: Tomorrow is my Talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 1472260.0,
      "end_time": 1475260.0,
      "text": "TD: Lakshmi has worked incredibly hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 1475260.0,
      "end_time": 1477260.0,
      "text": "even in inviting me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 1477260.0,
      "end_time": 1479260.0,
      "text": "let alone everything else that she has done"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 1479260.0,
      "end_time": 1481260.0,
      "text": "to make this happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1481260.0,
      "end_time": 1484260.0,
      "text": "and I was somewhat resistant at times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1484260.0,
      "end_time": 1487260.0,
      "text": "and I was also very nervous throughout this week."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1487260.0,
      "end_time": 1490260.0,
      "text": "I was feeling under the weather and dizzy and so forth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1490260.0,
      "end_time": 1492260.0,
      "text": "and people would ask me, why."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1492260.0,
      "end_time": 1495260.0,
      "text": "I would tell them, \"It&#39;s because I have to talk tomorrow.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1497260.0,
      "end_time": 1500260.0,
      "text": "And so Lakshmi had to put up with me through all of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1500260.0,
      "end_time": 1502260.0,
      "text": "but I very much appreciate"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1502260.0,
      "end_time": 1504260.0,
      "text": "the opportunity she&#39;s given me"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1504260.0,
      "end_time": 1506260.0,
      "text": "to be here."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1506260.0,
      "end_time": 1509260.0,
      "text": "And to you, everyone, thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
